## When to Refuse PRD Creation

If the initiative fails the strategic guardrails check, DO NOT create a PRD. Instead:

1. List the gaps/concerns clearly
2. Recommend specific discovery work
3. Suggest questions to answer first
4. Offer to help with discovery instead of PRD drafting
